### Ping
GET https://routelab.qzz.io/api/ping

### 上传轨迹示例
PUT https://routelab.qzz.io/api/routes/route_demo_1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "route_demo_1",
  "title": "Demo Walk",
  "startTime": 1734162523000,
  "endTime": 1734164323000,
  "privacyLevel": "group",
  "note": "示例数据",
  "campusZone": "理学院 · 教学区 · 一号楼",
  "startCampusMeta": {"category": "教学楼", "area": "东区", "location": "一号教学楼"},
  "endCampusMeta": {"category": "食堂", "area": "东区", "location": "第一食堂"},
  "activityType": "walk",
  "photos": [],
  "weight": 60,
  "points": [
    {"latitude": 30.0001, "longitude": 120.0002, "timestamp": 1734162523000},
    {"latitude": 30.0004, "longitude": 120.0006, "timestamp": 1734162623000}
  ],
  "stats": {"distance": 320, "duration": 100000, "speed": 3.2, "calories": 20}
}

### 修改为私密
PATCH https://routelab.qzz.io/api/routes/route_demo_1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "privacyLevel": "private"
}

### 删除示例
DELETE https://routelab.qzz.io/api/routes/route_demo_1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
